NAME
    Fuse::Template - Mount a template dir

SYNOPSIS
DESCRIPTION
ATTRIBUTES
  mountpoint
     $path = $self->mountpoint;

    Path to where the filesystem should be mounted.

    Required.

  mountopts
     $str = $self->mountopts;

    Default: "allow_other".

  debug
     $bool = $self->debug;

    Enable/disable debug output from Fuse. Default is disabled.

METHODS
  run
     $exit_code = $self->run;

    Starts Fuse's mainloop.

  find_file
     $real_path = $self->find_file($virtual_path);

    Returns path to the actual template file, from $virtual_path.

  log
     $bool = $self->log($level, $format, @args);

AUTHOR
    Jan Henning Thorsen

